title: [Patreon Preview] Pierogi Quesadilla
itunes:title: [Patreon Preview] Pierogi Quesadilla
description:
Got another zoom episode this week before reuniting in the studio next week! Listen to the gang breakdown negative reviews of Jim's stand-up, recall the story of Jim being upstaged by a bat, and get a tour of Forrest's hotel and pierogi quesadilla.

Subscribe at Patreon.com/IDKAT

Tiers start at $2 a month and come with perks ranging from ad-free IDKAT episodes, exclusive After Show episodes, and other bonus content!
